{"tid":2515414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息：荃威花園R座有外傭染疫　涉事家庭須隔離強制檢疫","createTime":"2021-05-04T03:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T03:34:00.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d30c7c3dfa22777d5f9f44d4db2488bdc242d000","tid":2515414,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"本港疫情受變種病毒流入社區出現變數，消息指位於荃灣荃威花園有外傭確診，涉事家庭須接受強制檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣區區議員趙恩來在其社交平台指出，昨晚荃威花園在傍晚6時許，有救護人員到R座接走一名外傭，前往接受詳細檢查。管業處已把R座2號升降機暫停關閉，直至專業清潔人員完成消毒工作。今早他再更新情況，指衞生署人員早上再到荃威花園R座接走一家四口，相信是前往隔離檢疫中心接受醫學觀察。<br />\n<br />\n趙恩來向TOPick表示，根據他了解，該名菲傭在3月底到港，期間曾經五次接受病毒測試，病毒檢測呈陰性，現時未知該名外傭是否感染了變種病毒。他亦正與民政署了解，是否需要全棟強制檢測或檢疫。<br />\n<br />\nTOPick正向衞生署了解情況。"},{"pid":"2d6e83d41c8be7764522882b2ea0d6081caab448","tid":2515414,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfM4G6dMDarK8oAp9ZXGJ3EHG47MUUvCfqpRha8p91uN8?filename=sA3tG4k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsA3tG4k.png&h=71409619&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44f45942e6eac6b096bfff00c8ef85a239fb77b1","tid":2515414,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"準備全座坐21日，記得自己帶定杯麵入去呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b83fa5317cd1440bebf8fdc5502cf9391d9648","tid":2515414,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:25:11.000Z","msg":"快走人<br />\n唔係轉頭又封<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b36cf98fcd3051122f6bf0cfadf3d7ad5392352","tid":2515414,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"趁777未出手<br />\n走人先<br />\n唔係21日<img src=\"/assets